{"tid":1006154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"出街遇到西人 你會點做","createTime":"2019-02-02T17:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T18:08:42.000Z","uid":185914,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a371b848c78526497aaef30b27fe192d34cb67a","tid":1006154,"uid":185914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"搭車隔離有對夫妻 40尾至50歲 睇個樣已經知係閪人<br />\n我同女朋友搭車傾計 唔太大聲<br />\n傾傾下聽到佢地話咩：佢地嘈我地咪嘈番佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個阿叔仲話：撞到我就批佢（我）踭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當時冇諗住作出咩回應 因為就算真係話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非佢搞到我/意圖同我正面衝突 否則我都唔諗住屌番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  淨係繼續同女朋友傾計<br />\n期間最多都係大家互望下 冇咩正面衝突<br />\n之後就到佢地落車 完。<br />\n<br />\n想表達 其實唔撚明呢D人咩心態 點解次次出街都當人地係仇人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算我真係嘈 屌你識唔撚識有禮貌咁表達？<br />\n又要屌 又要唔敢當面屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係算點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 如果你地出街遇同人正面衝突 你地又會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e08c50c69a33bd09ca43c26101fcb63d260366a","tid":1006154,"uid":41157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"仆街標題就話西人<br />\n內文原來係講閪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67d83ef02ad3498ca0689fc38ca69e7851f9f66","tid":1006154,"uid":157793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"你連粗口都唔敢打，睇唔出你會有咩作為喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f06e3ba08f3f5061309e96ee8d5ecb6bc2fbc4","tid":1006154,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"Nice to meet you"},{"pid":"